Definition claims that a brain's mere existence, is intelligence personified.
Have you seen society’s cogs lately?
They are an amalgam of cracks, crevices, grooves and scold
this organ donates itself to destruction, slowly capitulating to band aids, corners cut and proverbial blind eyes 

stretching, desperate-

Dendrites, ram horns
interlocking senders, impulses tinted dark, stained, demented
Freudian dissertation,
fixation focused- suck, fuck, satiating a deep seeded trust in regression

The guillotine, always sharpest on dead ends
Just a heady thought-Why am I here? 
Philosophical? Topical? Apocryphal?
Humour us, as the organ stumbles through this dance

Forgetful- since slipping on purpose
Scattered- losing sequential precious steps
Muscle memory, once assured, now ulterior deterioration
Seized surrender, hypoxia-laced stoned 
Divine’s ultimate detonation engaged- 
Be a thinking enemy.

-  Shallow and Angela Murray 

